name: AutoSoftener (4Mb)
description:
1 click and let the magic happens!

you can choose a weight from 1.0 to 2.0

my default suggestion would be 1.5

this LoRA will make your images better (and softer).

it doesn't need any prompt to activate it.

___________

Visit My Patreon if you want to support me. I'm also accepting LoRA Commissions & Requests.
